    </p></statement>
    <answer><p><ol label="a">
        <li><p>Scale factor <m>-3 </m>; <m>y =\sqrt{v}</m> is reflected over the <m>v</m>-axis and stretched vertically by a factor of <m>3</m>.</p></li>
        <li><p><image source="images/fig-ans-2-3-27"  width="45%"><description>transformed root</description></image> </p></li>
    </ol></p></answer>
    </exercise>

    <exercise number="28"><statement><p>
        <m>g(z)=\dfrac{2}{z} </m>
