        <li><p>Scale factor <m>\frac{-1}{2} </m>; <m>y =s^3 </m> is reflected over the <m>s</m>-axis and compressed vertically by a factor of <m>\frac{1}{2}</m>.</p></li>
        <li><p><image source="images/fig-ans-2-3-29"  width="45%"><description>transformed cubic</description></image> </p></li>
    </ol></p></answer>
    </exercise>

    <exercise number="30"><statement><p>
