<exercise number="37"><statement><p>
    <sidebyside width="80%"><image source="images/fig-2-3-37"><description> graph and 4 transformations</description></image> </sidebyside>
</p></statement>
<answer><p><ol label="a">
    <li><p>Reflected about the <m>v</m>-axis and stretched vertically by a factor of <m>2</m>: <m>T = -2h(v)</m></p></li>
    <li><p>Stretched vertically by a factor of <m>3</m>: <m>T = 3h(v)</m></p></li>
    <li><p>Translated <m>3</m> units up: <m>T = h(v) + 3</m></p></li>
    <li><p>Translated <m>3</m> units left: <m>T = h(v + 3)</m></p></li>
</ol></p></answer>
</exercise>

